name: FingerPunk #025 (Crypto Wizard)
description: Crypto Wizard is an esoteric sage and has a line of communication open with the architect of the metaverse. The other FingerPunks regard him highly and seek his advice when anything strange happens. He recently held a conference where he alluded to a destabilizing force threatening their world. He promised to learn more about this potential cataclysm and find a way to prevent it. Crypto Wizard is the second epic FingerPunk.
